{"tid":2029152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"7.28上環案 速龍小隊指揮官潘誦騏首次出庭作供","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T07:32:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"016a06dc92dd5f8af7b0255dbd5d4c875923fe5d","tid":2029152,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200522/PPVA36BI5RTKV2B5S7IO5ERD54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2FPPVA36BI5RTKV2B5S7IO5ERD54%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=162eaa1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200522%2FPPVA36BI5RTKV2B5S7IO5ERD54%2F&h=12557f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200522/PPVA36BI5RTKV2B5S7IO5ERD54/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/G3lQcmCB6GrPQaU86xrKdnLWNGI=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PDS2C6IHG7LKTLQQB6HVYN4RPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FG3lQcmCB6GrPQaU86xrKdnLWNGI%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPDS2C6IHG7LKTLQQB6HVYN4RPA.jpg&h=78f9f868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反修例運動首宗暴動案審訊，今早續審。控方上周五要求法庭批准四名速龍小隊成員及一名署理警長作供時，利用特別通道出入法庭，以免他們因樣貌曝光而影響工作，遭辯方批評此舉目的只為躲避傳媒拍攝。控方今早撤回申請，表示會以「另一方式」處理相關「擔憂」。主審法官郭啟安直指控方應在審前覆核時提出申請，如今做法是浪費法庭時間，揚言會考慮追究控方。辯方則透露，控方早於今年3月13日已簽署確認書，表明不會為證人申請以特別通道出入。"},{"pid":"5b1706c00e0076043c15dcf74b490dced76f4ec6","tid":2029152,"uid":328890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce6f16e95aadb2e2bf3aebd6a7bbc3935594795f","tid":2029152,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b1706c00e0076043c15dcf74b490dced76f4ec6","tid":2029152,"uid":3